LyondellBasell




Mr. Buchanan is a Senior Advisor at Bain & Company Inc., the worldwide business consulting firm. He also serves on the board of directors of Schroders plc. and is a Director of the Centre for Corporate Governance at London Business School where he previously served as Dean and then President.













