Management Board
Supervisory Board
Leadership Team














The Management Board is led by its Chairman, our Chief Executive Officer Bhavesh V. (Bob) Patel. It is responsible for management of LyondellBasell and the implementation of its corporate strategy. The Management Board is made up of executives of LyondellBasell, appointed by shareholders upon the nomination by the Supervisory Board.






















Bhavesh V. (Bob) Patel
Chief Executive Officer and Chairman, Management Board
