Insider Activity


Individual




Robin W. T. Buchanan



Mr. Robin W. Buchanan is Independent Class II Member-Supervisory Board at LyondellBasell Industries NV, Director-Centre Corporate Governance at London Business School and a Member at The Trilateral Commission. He is on the Board of Directors at LyondellBasell Industries NV and Schroders Plc. Mr. Buchanan was previously employed as Chairman by Michael Page International Plc, Non-Executive Director by Shire Plc /Old/, Non-Executive Director by Liberty International Plc, a Principal by American Express Bank Ltd., Senior Partner by Bain & Co., Inc. (London), a Principal by McKinsey & Co., Inc., and Non-Executive Director by Shire Acquisition, Inc. He also served on the board at Boron, LePore & Associates, Inc. He received his MBA from Harvard Business School.



